init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You know what you must do.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are in a room with a desk, a phone, and a computer.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You arrive in a strange room with a strange looking man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He says, "Welcome to the future, Barack.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm here to stop the extinction of the dinosaurs?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: stop the extinction of the dinosaurs."
